org.dspace.statistics.service

Interface ElasticSearchLoggerService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ElasticSearchLoggerServiceImpl

    public interface ElasticSearchLoggerService
    Service interface class for the Elastic Search logging. The implementation of this class is responsible for all business logic calls for the Elastic Search logging and is autowired by spring
    Author:
    kevinvandevelde at atmire.com
